# Search Indices

Searching for content about something? Try one of these!
(Unlike Google, these won't understand questions - be sure your search includes the actual words that should be in the found pages (and no other words))

=> gemini://tlgs.one "Totally Legit" Gemini Search (for Geminispace)
=> gopher://gopher.floodgap.com/1/v2/ Floodgap/Veronica 2 (for Gopherspace)

